7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both BlueWillow and StarryAI share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Image, Upscaling, Commercial License. On the other hand, StarryAI uniquely offers Style Transfer, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, BlueWillow holds an overall score of 4/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while StarryAI scores 5/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both BlueWillow and StarryAI offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. BlueWillow's free tier and StarryAI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
