b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. BlueWillow is best suited for free image generation, beginners, Discord users, experimentation, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. StarryAI, meanwhile, shines for mobile art creation, NFT art, casual generation, on the go creativity, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2023, BlueWillow describes itself as \"Free AI image generator accessible through Discord.\" StarryAI, established in 2021, positions itself as \"Mobile-first AI art generator with NFT minting support.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **StarryAI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (5.0 vs 4.0), more features (4 vs 3), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean BlueWillow is a poor choice — far from it. BlueWillow excels in its own right, particularly for free image generation and beginners.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value good mobile app experience, go with StarryAI. If free to use with decent quality matters more to you, BlueWillow is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
